  <p><em>Last Updated: August 2025</em></p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may temporarily collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your Telegram user ID</li>
    <li>Your public username</li>
    <li>Messages you send to the bot or in groups it moderates</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Info</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your commands</li>
    <li>To moderate group chats</li>
    <li>To improve community engagement</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your data. Hosting providers may process it only to run the bot.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We keep logs only temporarily for debugging or moderation.</p>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Contact us at <a href="https://t.me/AviryxNest">Aviryx Telegram</a>.</p>
